snippet.title: The Sims 4 Toddler Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Give your toddlers new ways to express their personalities, burn off energy, and make friends!

Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://x.ea.com/33484

Dress your little Sims in a variety of adorable outfits and cute hairstyles. Use colorful décor to build an outdoor play space where toddlers can enjoy the slide, crawling tunnels, and ball pit with friends.

#sims4
